description.text: Welcome to 1424 Lakeland Drive. This inviting property offers the best of country living on 1.3 acres of lush gardens and mature landscape with room to spare. Exterior features include a detached two car garage, utility shed, screened in back porch, open deck, and stone patio. All within walking distance to Lakeland High School. Inside you're greeted by a spacious mudroom, refined kitchen, and cozy family/living rooms. The main level is complete with 1 bed, 1 bath, laundry hook-up, wood stove, and fireplace. Continuing upstairs you'll find three well maintained bedrooms and a full bathroom with no lack of charm. Peace of mind is guaranteed with a generator compatible outlet capable of powering the entire home, B-Dry & sub-pump systems, and a multitude of heating options. These options include: Oil/steam furnace, wood stove, pellet stove, fireplace, and electric baseboard. Showings begin Monday, August 14th.
